{"tid":989413,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[旅保] 兩份旅保可唔可以同時claim?","createTime":"2019-01-20T23:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T23:55:03.000Z","uid":84508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9b4d0fee6e816ab77eadb7f4ab69ae8489f112","tid":989413,"uid":84508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:49:20.000Z","msg":"本身張信用卡去旅行已經包左份保險<br />\n之後如果自己再買第二間既旅保<br />\n<br />\n咁出事可唔可以claim兩間？<br />\n二月尾去北海道 揸車怕出事 怕撞<br />\n諗住買多份保障下  有咩情況可以claim兩份<br />\n<br />\n聽講身故同delay 都可以claim 兩份<br />\n但撞車 相機 電腦 跌爛有無得claim 兩邊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c12de06e6a719f493defc8b7c89d5d1b0abbec","tid":989413,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:50:14.000Z","msg":"怕撞咪唔好揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beecafd64204335f859e0070ec75d175e4abdb8f","tid":989413,"uid":23923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:52:51.000Z","msg":"保額唔同既話claim完細份可以claim埋大份個差額"},{"pid":"549798ef33ee7220e6630b4e6ed59c55d7828b61","tid":989413,"uid":119409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc9b4d0fee6e816ab77eadb7f4ab69ae8489f112","tid":989413,"uid":84508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:49:20.000Z","msg":"本身張信用卡去旅行已經包左份保險<br />\n之後如果自己再買第二間既旅保<br />\n<br />\n咁出事可唔可以claim兩間？<br />\n二月尾去北海道 揸車怕出事 怕撞<br />\n諗住買多份保障下  有咩情況可以claim兩份<br />\n<br />\n聽講身故同delay 都可以claim 兩份<br />\n但撞車 相機 電腦 跌爛有無得claim 兩邊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:53:12.000Z","msg":"好似唔可以全數<br />\n所以通常保險公司有條約係鼓勵你claim第二間先<br />\n就可以比啲 bonus你"},{"pid":"9b0af71a14bd4b1eecb2782a9474c6ba9d1905ab","tid":989413,"uid":82791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T23:55:03.000Z","msg":"你講既都可以claim兩邊但唔會賠多過個樣野既價值。例如相機值$5000,一份最多賠$3000,另一份可以賠埋個$2000，當然都要睇條款啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}